						<summary>

						<p>This is built in at the beginning of each line. It seems to record an agreement by the assembly of <hi rend="bold">Nandikampa-chaturvēdimaṅgalam</hi> in Pāli-nāḍu a subdivision of Paḍuvūr-kōṭṭam to remove the silt from the local tank every year to the extent of 20 <hi rend="italic">kuḻi</hi> with the interest on seven (?) <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold received by them from a resident of <hi rend="bold">Iṟaiyāṉsēri in Kachchippēḍu.</hi></p>						

